h2.div: Rio Community School District will be closed indefinitely!

h3.div: 3/20/20 WI DPI Internet at Home Survey

div.class: hJDwNd-AhqUyc-qWD73c jXK9ad D2fZ2 OjCsFc wHaque GNzUNc

h3.div: We are Rio Community Schools, a small and very vibrant district in southern Columbia County. Every student at Rio is invited to choose to excel. Our small class size encourages individual involvement and interaction between staff and students, helping to ensure all students grow. Our small school culture allows for abundant opportunity to be active in many extracurricular activities including athletics, clubs, music, forensics and community outreach. Parents and community members are continually engaged in our schools as volunteers and supporters, creating a deep partnership between the school community and the greater Rio area that many other districts envy. We invite you to visit Rio Schools.

small.style: display: block; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;
small.strong: It is the mission of the Rio Community School District to provide a healthy, safe and engaging environment in which each student participates in a high-quality education that he or she will use to grow as a person and become an active contributor to our community and the world.

h3.div: Wisconsin Department of Public Instruction District Report Card
